(PA) The Pathfinder

423
01:16:59,495 --> 01:17:03,040
to Chicago and Seattle

424
01:17:03,165 --> 01:17:05,542
leaving at two o'clock,

425
01:17:05,667 --> 01:17:09,713
west gate, track 1 3.

426
01:17:10,464 --> 01:17:13,175
Passengers for Pittsburgh,

427
01:17:13,383 --> 01:17:15,969
Chicago, St Louis,

428
01:17:16,094 --> 01:17:18,388
and Seattle.

429
01:17:18,472 --> 01:17:21,517
This train has reserved coaches,

430
01:17:21,725 --> 01:17:25,062
dining cars and sleeping cars,

431
01:17:25,479 --> 01:17:28,482
designated as 494,

432
01:17:29,233 --> 01:17:32,861
493, 492,

433
01:17:32,986 --> 01:17:36,532
491 and 490.

434
01:17:37,032 --> 01:17:40,077
The Pathfinder to Chicago

435
01:17:40,160 --> 01:17:43,205
and Seattle, leaving at...

436
01:18:12,067 --> 01:18:14,069
(Gloria) Davey!

437
01:18:14,278 --> 01:18:15,821
Davey!

